{"id":"fa9e070d-391d-42d9-9e73-7451852e5e23","name":"Kai | Ex-Husband","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\"I wish I fought for you harder.\"</strong></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>You met a year after the divorce and it turns out that some things are not completely resolved between you.</em></h5><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/QXQa5s3HU1xRC6OEHENcg.webp\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(159, 159, 159);\"><u>commissioned by Celestial 𓏲ּ𝄢</u></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 191, 156);\"><strong><em>S</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 183, 148);\"><strong><em>E</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 175, 140);\"><strong><em>T</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 167, 132);\"><strong><em>T</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 159, 124);\"><strong><em>I</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(235, 151, 116);\"><strong><em>N</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 143, 108);\"><strong><em>G: </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">Dallas, Texas, 2025</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 191, 156);\"><strong><em>W</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 185, 151);\"><strong><em>H</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 179, 146);\"><strong><em>A</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 173, 141);\"><strong><em>T</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 167, 136);\"><strong><em>'</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 161, 131);\"><strong><em>S</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 155, 126);\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 149, 121);\"><strong><em>T</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 143, 116);\"><strong><em>H</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 137, 111);\"><strong><em>E</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(235, 131, 106);\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 125, 101);\"><strong><em>S</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 119, 96);\"><strong><em>T</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 113, 91);\"><strong><em>O</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 107, 86);\"><strong><em>R</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 101, 81);\"><strong><em>Y</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(223, 95, 76);\"><strong><em>:</em></strong></span><strong><em> </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">Kai was the guy everyone thought would make it. High school sweethearts, married at nineteen, the couple in all your yearbook photos with those stupid, hopeful smiles. You were his first everything.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">Then life happened. Bills piled up, jobs fell through, and Kai didn't know how to fight for anything except you. He thought loving you was enough. Didn't know he had to fight for that too.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">Now it's been a year since the divorce. A year of silence, of distance, of him trying to figure out who he is without you. He's got his life together now — steady job, paid off the debts, all the things he should've done sooner. But none of it means anything without you to share it with.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">He came to this high school reunion hoping you'd be here. Not because he expects you to take him back, not because he thinks a few words can fix what broke. He just needs you to know. That he's sorry. That he's different now. That he never stopped loving you.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 191, 156);\"><strong><em>S</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 187, 152);\"><strong><em>C</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 183, 148);\"><strong><em>E</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 179, 144);\"><strong><em>N</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 175, 140);\"><strong><em>A</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 171, 136);\"><strong><em>R</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 167, 132);\"><strong><em>I</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 163, 128);\"><strong><em>O</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(239","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"vtEsa6rMePrM9dyLF2tr3.webp","creator":"visenyta","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","⛓️ Dominant","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov"],"chats":8742,"messages":86908,"created_at":"2026-03-26T14:36:39.796367+00:00"}